{{!
    @template format_tiles/tileicon

    Tile icon template.

    The purpose of this template is to render a single icon for a tile
    to be displayed in the tile template

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
        * editing - is the user editing
        * secid - which section id in the sections table, not just the tile num in this course
        * tileid - which tile num in this course
        * title: - the section title for the icon alt text

    Example context (json):
    {
        "editing": 0,
        "secid": 33,
        "tileid": 3,
        "title": "Introduction"
    }
}}
